data.description: Lovingly improved & meticulously maintained, this home is the definition of better than new! Sought after floor plan w/ 3 bedrooms up + spacious main floor office & lofted upstairs bonus room.  Complete renovation in 2021 included new LVP flooring thru the main floor, quartz countertops & all new stainless appliances in kitchen, fresh interior paint downstairs & in garage, new exterior paint, new AC, new 6 ft cedar fencing, new hot tub & artificial turf front & back. New tankless hot water & epoxy on garage floors added in 2022. W/D also new in 2021 stays w/the home. All this in a popular neighborhood of other well kept homes. Enjoy huge community park, walking trails & easy Hwy 18 access. Don’t let this one get away!
